"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"尽管有储备资金的存在，但与MakerDAO不同，Celo的稳定币并非超额抵押铸造而来，而是通过向官方稳定模块Mento发Celo代币而获得，用户发送1美元价值的Celo，可以获得1美元的cUSD等稳定币，也可以反向向Mento发送1美元价值的cUSD，换回1美元的Celo。在这种机制下，当cUSD市价低于1美元，就会有人低价买入cUSD去换得1美元Celo，同理当cUSD高于1美元时，就会有人用Celo铸造cUSD去卖出，套利者的存在会保证cUSD不会偏离其锚定价格太远。\\n\\n[https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1NDQ0MzY5Mg==&mid=2247484686&idx=1&sn=75089a556937759bc86dd67a598311cb&scene=21#wechat_redirect](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1NDQ0MzY5Mg==&mid=2247484686&idx=1&sn=75089a556937759bc86dd67a598311cb&scene=21#wechat_redirect)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Zxiy89wkm858knRRFIY5T.png?height=558&width=1454)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637321441,\"title\":\"celo 套利\"},\"digest\":\"6Z98CowDsTFLIX1m5_t-Uaqt8epIidZ4iiGlifJn2Pk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe9A9903DB6d7341f03a933C048aaf3D49a49CFb1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"yDWi20K0UayA1oEy6xJ_KNme-i9ciLtizsyjI5f5RWA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3lStSklxqe1GfkvGWjXaUklklCRTeeDrF7OjZ1hfGdo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"R4DwXMBNKoHkgxTvpYM4VXMHf6MXe7Dd4cIlZghi2U25EpS905hsjlg2PduOUn99sS90LvrE4RkHWcWBSIpPtQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4cba847867a304023b5ce92e7aa9e76535bd704db5f28b15dbeca724b6228ce964ba33303a89ef399c8792dcbed27759a31353dd7db33fe898d963984df4b10a1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"yDWi20K0UayA1oEy6xJ_KNme-i9ciLtizsyjI5f5RWA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3lStSklxqe1GfkvGWjXaUklklCRTeeDrF7OjZ1hfGdo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"n_uvhAq8SDSAfFksfQgl6EyCfBWzxL8JbAp7SKS0u2U\"}"